	(text "============================================\nDESIGN NOTE: 6N137 INPUT DRIVE CALCULATION\n============================================\nSource Voltage (Vcc): 3.3V\nSwitch: 2N2222 NPN (Low-Side)\n\nPARAMETERS:\n- Opto Vf: 1.4V (min) to 1.7V (max)\n- Transistor Vce(sat): ~0.2V\n- Target Current (If): 10mA - 20mA (Safe Zone)\n\nCALCULATION:\nR_min = (3.3V - 1.7V - 0.2V) / 20mA = 70 Ω\nR_max = (3.3V - 1.4V - 0.2V) / 10mA = 170 Ω\n\nSELECTED VALUE: 100 Ω (Standard E24)\n- Estimated Current @ 1.55V Vf: ~15.5mA\n- Power Dissipation: ~24mW (Standard 0603/0805 OK)\n============================================\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 109.982 27.686 0)
